# isRegistered

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value that indicates whether the postback is registered in the testing environment.

## Declaration

```swift
var isRegistered: Bool { get }
```

## Discussion

To register a postback, call [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/StoreKit/SKAdNetwork/updatePostbackConversionValue(_:completionHandler:)], or [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/StoreKit/SKAdNetwork/registerAppForAdNetworkAttribution()].

## Getting general information

- **version**: The SKAdNetwork version that the postback uses.
- **transactionIdentifier**: A unique transaction identifier that the system generates.
- **postbackSequenceIndex**: The position of this postback among all postbacks for an ad impression.
- **isRedownload**: A Boolean value that indicates whether the user redownloaded and reinstalled the app.
